Class Symbol

Created 10-1010

Changelog available at Symbol.

java.lang.Object
  Symbol
All Implemented Interfaces:
SymbolInterface
public class Symbol
extends java.lang.Object
implements SymbolInterface

Contains all necessary data about a symbol for the symbol table, as represented by a label, a location, a length, and a usage type. NOTE: DO NOT CONFUSE THE SYMBOL'S NAME IN JAVA WITH ITS LABEL IN SAL560

Author:
Jeff W
